web_snippets: Colby Blaine is an American college basketball coach who is the head coach of the College of Idaho Coyotes men's basketball team.
Colby Blaine began coaching at the College of Idaho in 2014, initially as an assistant coach. He was promoted to associate head coach before the 2016-17 season.
